sylvia is a 2003 british biographical drama film directed by christine jeffs and starring gwyneth paltrow , daniel craig , jared harris , and michael gambon .   it tells the true story of the romance between prominent poets sylvia plath and ted hughes .   the film begins with their meeting at cambridge in 1956 and ends with sylvia plath 's suicide in 1963 .   frieda hughes , sylvia and ted 's daughter , accused the filmmakers of profiting from her mother 's death .